net.sqlcipher

Interface Cursor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCursor, AbstractWindowedCursor, BulkCursorToCursorAdaptor, CrossProcessCursorWrapper, CursorWrapper, MatrixCursor, SQLiteCursor

    public interface Cursor
    Extension of android.database.Cursor to support getType() for API < 11.

    • Method Detail

      • getType

        int getType(int columnIndex)
        Returns data type of the given column's value. The preferred type of the column is returned but the data may be converted to other types as documented in the get-type methods such as #getInt(int), #getFloat(int) etc.

        Returned column types are

        • FIELD_TYPE_NULL
        • FIELD_TYPE_INTEGER
        • FIELD_TYPE_FLOAT
        • FIELD_TYPE_STRING
        • FIELD_TYPE_BLOB

        Parameters:
        columnIndex - the zero-based index of the target column.
        Returns:
        column value type
